Author: hypotheticalfox
Text: Totally understand, my upside to getting a cavity filled is that I can't eat for the rest of the day...

Author: eminelope
Text: No, I completely understand. I don’t have the flu, but I’ve got a cold with a bit of a fever right now and I’ve lost 4lbs from a lack of appetite (the only time that will ever happen). Sure, I feel like crap, but it also feels so gooood!
